About this item

  • Smart Motion Sensing Technology: With a 10-foot, 120-degree sensing range, our motion sensor light indoor activates upon detecting movement, providing hands-free convenience. After 20 seconds of no motion, it automatically switches off to conserve energy.
  • Eye-Care Gradual Brightening: Our under cabinet lights gradually brighten to avoid sudden glare, providing gentle illumination that safeguards your eyes.
  • 60 Straight-Emitting LEDs: Compared to side-emitting, our under counter lights for kitchen offer higher luminous efficiency and greater energy savings, ensuring superior brightness while consuming less power.
  • Long-lasting Illumination: Featuring a high-capacity battery, our rechargeable battery operated lights offer up to 60 days of continuous use in sensor mode, addressing your need for lighting without frequent charging.
  • 4 Lighting Modes: Choose from four versatile modes: always on, day, night, and off. Day mode activates when motion sensed in all light conditions, night mode activates when motion sensed in low light conditions, ensuring energy efficiency and light only when you need it.
  • Adjustable Brightness Levels: According to your preference, tap for 4-level dimming from 25%, 50%, 75%, or 100% brightness options, long press for seamless dimming adjustment, providing the perfect under cabinet lighting for any occasion.
  • Effortless Installation: Equipped with built-in magnets and additional adhesive metal plates, our closet lights can be easily installed on any surface with no tools required. Enjoy enhanced lighting in minutes wherever you need illumination.
  • Versatile Application: Perfect for under cabinet lighting wireless in kitchens, wardrobes, bedrooms, stairwells or hallways, enhancing every corner of your home.
  • Sleek, Ultra-Thin Design: Our latest generation led lights for bedroom features a full-screen, ultra-thin design at just 0.39 inches thick, blending seamlessly into your home decor.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
